	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>One thing to recall about shaman before you scoff at our melee.&nbsp;&nbsp;A shaman has access to most of the best melee buffs in the game, as well as a 50% haste spell (celerity + silver chitin gaunts = 72% self haste). To be honest, if I want to solo almost manaless I can pull a dark blue with slow and beat the poo out of a mob while my pet chews on its arse.  I have had my atk over 1200 without rabid bear (using primal avatar), strength and dex easily hit 255 each with just foc and VoB.  <br><br>A shaman can stand toe-to-toe with most of the soloing type blue mobs and flat melee it to death.  Which I will add is more than quite a few warriors and other meleers can do.  We can also finish that fight close to full mana and hp thanks to torpor.  I have been looking for a good haste item that the meleers didnt have first shot at for a while.  This looks like it may be a good target.<br>&nbsp;<br>Mathi Bear<br>Oracle of Justice<br>&lt;Fallen Legacy&gt;<br>Lany's</td></tr>
